pieces of wood should he fetch at first?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p></p>','<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp;</span>In the first line ,there are one integer N (0&lt;N&lt;=100000),indicating that there are N cases totally.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count:1\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Then N lines flows.Each line consists of two integers,K and S (1&lt;=K&lt;=S&lt;=1000000).<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p></p>','<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">For each case ,If John will be successful , output a integer M in a line,indicating that John shoule fetch M piece(s) of wood in the first fetch;else output &ldquo;Regretful&rdquo;in a line.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p></p>','2\r\n1 2\r\n2 26\r\n','Regretful\r\n2\r\n','0','','西南科技大学月赛','2011-06-02 20:58:44',1,128,'N',7,42,0,1),(1280,'Mr.Yang’s course','<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt\">Mr.yang</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">是一位优秀的算法课教师，他非常注重学生的动手能力。因此，他通过在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt\">judge online</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">平台上布置作业来检查学生的学习情况，并依据做题情况给定学生的成绩排名。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;\r\nmso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count:\r\n1\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Mr.yang</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-ascii-font-f